title: Elves #02 - The Wood Elves&rsquo; Honor (2013) (Alice) cbz
description:
The city of Eysine is besieged by Orc mercenaries. The situation is so desperate that the daughter of the king decides, against all advice, to go seek the help of the Wood Elves.

Ambushed and pursued deeper and deeper into the forest by Orcs, she takes refuge in the ruins of a sanctuary jealously guarded by the Elves. When the ancient power that haunts the place recognizes the young woman as the last descendant of the Druids, her adventure truly begins...
